&amp; Gilbert, 1879:386 (corrected to 
<taxonomicName box="[734,846,1866,1888]" class="Elasmobranchii" family="Dasyatidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Myliobatiformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="353" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Dasyatidae</taxonomicName>
